94
00:05:21,090 --> 00:05:22,090
Isang pervert?

95
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:24,659
Halika na. katawa-tawa yan.

96
00:05:24,660 --> 00:05:26,899
"Sa tuwing hinihiling kong matulog sa iyo..."

97
00:05:26,900 --> 00:05:28,969
Ay naku.

98
00:05:28,970 --> 00:05:31,399
