113
00:06:17,010 --> 00:06:18,820
Hoy, kayo.

114
00:06:19,180 --> 00:06:21,719
May alam ka bang lugar na may Giant sa pangalan?

115
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:24,520
Tulad ng Giant Arcade o isang bagay,

116
00:06:24,820 --> 00:06:27,260
